~ cactus
: It's a small cactus! I'll have to be careful when picking it up...

if State.temp_inventory.has("strange_plant"):
	: But my hands are full since I'm already carrying this other plant...
	=> END

: Take this plant?
- Yes
	: You took the plant.
	do State.temp_inventory.append("cactus")
- Leave it
=> END 

~ strange_plant
: A potted plant...
: If Ray likes gardening, then he might like this one.
if State.temp_inventory.has("cactus"):
	: But my hands are full since I'm already carrying this cactus...
	=> END

: Take this plant? 
- Yes
	: You took the plant.
	do State.temp_inventory.append("strange_plant")
- Leave it 
