~ produce
: It's a bunch of colorful fruits and veggies!
=> END

~ carrots
: Ooh, carrots. I could make some stew from these.
: Take the carrots? 
- Yes
	: You took the carrots.
	do State.temp_inventory.append("carrots")
- No
=> END 

~ bunny_body
if not (State.rabbit_amount == 2):
	if State.rabbit_amount == 0:
		: ...Well, I guess this one will do.
		: Looks like a good catch. 
		: I'll need another one if I want to make some rabbit stew.
	elseif State.rabbit_amount == 1:
		: Nice!
		: This one is good.
		: I hope Ray likes it.
	
	set State.rabbit_amount += 1
	if State.rabbit_amount == 2:
		do QuestManager.emit_signal("got_rabbits")
else:
	: I won't need any more rabbits to make stew.
=> END